description	"BX Commando Droid

Class Summary:
An agile class with a balanced outfit of tools and abilities.

Weapons:
- E-5 Blaster BX Custom (Based on EE-3 level 2)
- Vibrosword *
- Incendiary Grenades (2)

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
---Vibrosword
- Defense (1)
- Regenerates BP passively
- Melee weapon based on Lightsaber
- Deals reduced damage
- Cannot block blaster fire
- Can block lightsabers 
- Can use Yellow and Red styles

Attributes:
- Shield Recharge (1)
- Blast Armour
- Magnetic Plating
- Strong against Physical Damage
- Radar (Perma-sense 1)
- 3x Faster Force Regen

Force Powers:
- Jump (2)

Abilities:
- Dash (2)

BX-series commando droids were advanced, sturdier versions of B1 battle droids. They were programmed with improved combat tactics and battlefield awareness and equipped with glowing white photoreceptors. Captains and other high-ranking commando droids bore white identifiers on their heads and chests."